      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHADOW REAPER (2) has an excellent record over this journey having never missed the placings in four starts, including three wins. Scored by 4.5 lengths last time (34.75) in a Grade 5 over 601m at this track. Looks suited and should go close. INCREDIBLE ROGUE (4) was below best last time finishing sixth at this track, but prior to that had been racing well including a Free For All win two back at Northam. Can turn it around this time. BROOKMAN RANGER (6) collided with another runner and finished a well held 8 lengths fourth (35.31) last time in a Grade 5 at this track over 601m. Has the ability and can measure up. JUST A PRINCESS (8) jumps at a shorter distance and still warrants respect.",
